default&#xa0;
defaultQ6 default&#xa0; 
defaultChair:default And how would you describe its trajectory at the moment?
defaultSir Michael Wilshawdefault: Unless particular issues are sorted out, I would say it is going to remain on grade three.  
default&#xa0;
defaultQ7 default&#xa0; 
defaultChair:default So it is coasting at an unacceptable level.
defaultSir Michael Wilshawdefault: It is coasting at an unacceptable level, and unless leadership improves, unless turnover decreases in terms of leadership of directors of children’s services, unless the safeguarding boards’ roles and responsibilities are properly defined, and unless the issues of recruitment of social workers in parts of the world 
defaultsuch as 
defaultBirmingham are addressed, the situation will continue as it is.  
