defaultQ9 default&#xa0; 
defaultAlex Cunningham:default Despite the lack of social care credentials in the overall team.
defaultSir Michael Wilshawdefault: If I can tell you what we have done, certainly in my time in office, we have increased the number of senior HMI by nearly 50%; we have appointed an outstanding Director of Children’s Services to lead those HMI; we have increased the number of HMI; we have regionalised them into our eight 
defaultOfsted
default regions; we have appointed more regulatory inspectors and done something about the performance management of a significant number of weak regulatory inspectors—
default&#xa0;
defaultQ10 default&#xa0; 
