defaultDebbie Jonesdefault: I would say that inevitably, when a child dies in difficult circumstances, there is interest from the public and from the media.  
defaultIt is important that w
defaulte are clear that you do not just get the learning from the high-profile cases; you get the learning from the other in
default&#x2011;
